### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health

### Login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "U100",
  "password": "demo123456"
}

### Metrics overview
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/metrics/overview

### Recommendation compare
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/recommend/compare
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "U100",
  "top_k": 20,
  "query": "AI regulation"
}

### Strategy evaluation
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/evaluate/strategies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "k_values": [5, 10, 20]
}

### Train LTR model
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/models/ltr/train
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "max_users": 400,
  "epochs": 90,
  "learning_rate": 0.08
}

### LTR model status
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/models/ltr/status

### LTR recommendation
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/recommend/ltr
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "U100",
  "top_k": 20,
  "hybrid_rag": true
}

### Recommendation explanation
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/me/recommend/explain/N1006
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Ablation
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/evaluate/ablation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "U100",
  "top_k": 20
}

### Experiments
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/experiments

### Hybrid RAG query
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/me/rag/hybrid-query
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "新闻推荐系统为什么需要推荐透明度？",
  "top_k": 5
}

### Agent trace
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/me/agent/trace
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "结合我的资料库，推荐并解释几篇 AI 监管相关的新闻",
  "top_k": 5
}
